Into 50 µl of the sample, add
- 200 µl of 12% / 0.32% acrylamide / bisacryloylcystamine
- 25 µl of 10% ammoniumpersulfate
Vortex into 600 µl of Span/Tween/Triton oil.
- Add 25 µl TEMED and vortex. Extract with diethylether after 1.5 h polymerization. Wash with water until clear.

Span/Tween/Triton oil
- 2,25 ml Span 80
- 200 µl Tween 80
- 25 µl Triton X-100
Mineral oil to 50 ml

Emulsion fusion PCR:
|----------+---------+----------------------|
| 1X       | 2X      |                      |
|----------+---------+----------------------|
| 10 µl    | 20 μl   | 5X HF                |
| 1 µl     | 2 μl    | 50 mM MgCl2          |
| 1.25 µl  | 2.5 μl  | 10 mM dNTP           |
| 5 µl     | 10 μl   | 10 µM primer 9       |
| 5 µl     | 10 μl   | 10 µM primer 5       |
| 0.5 µl   | 1 μl    | 1 µM primer 2        |
| 23.25 µl | 46.5 μl | polyacrylamide beads |
| 4 µl     | 8 μl    | Phusion              |
|----------+---------+----------------------|
Add 450 µl of mineral oil with 4% Abil EM 90
Vortex into an emulsion with 4 1 mm glass beads

1. 94°C 30 seconds
2. 94°C 5 seconds
3. 52°C 30 seconds
4. 72°C 45 seconds
5. Move to step 2. 32 times
6. 72°C 5 minutes

|-----------+--------------------------+-----------------------------------------|
| Zurich ix | Name                     | Sequence                                |
|-----------+--------------------------+-----------------------------------------|
|         9 | 1492R                    | GGTTACCTTGTTACGACTT                     |
|         5 | 18S 1629-1647 for        | AGCGACGGGCGGTGTGTAC                     |
|         2 | 18S 1266-1286 for - 519R | GWATTACCGCGGCKGCTGTGGTGGTGCATGGCCGTTCTT |
|-----------+--------------------------+-----------------------------------------|

Extract twice with water-saturated diethylether (~2 ml), once with water-saturated ethylacetate (~2 ml) and twice more with water-saturated diethylether (~1 ml).

Purify the fusion reaction using AMPure beads: into 100 µl of the extracted reaction, add 100 µl of AMPure slurry. Incubate 10 min. Wash 2X with 400 µl of 70% EtOH. Dry 1 min and suspend into 50 µl water.

|---------+--------+-----------------------------|
| 1X      | 3X     |                             |
|---------+--------+-----------------------------|
| 7.25 μl | 29. μl | H2O                         |
| 5 μl    | 20 μl  | 5x Phusion HF Buffer        |
| 0.5 μl  | 2. μl  | 10 mM dNTPs                 |
| 2.5 μl  | 10. μl | 3 µM primer 10              |
| 2.5 μl  | 10. μl | 3 µM primer 146             |
| 2.5 μl  | 10. μl | 32 µM primer 16             |
| 2.5 μl  | 10. μl | 32 µM primer 17             |
| 0.25 μl | 1 μl   | Phusion HF Polymerase 2U/µl |
|---------+--------+-----------------------------|

1. 98°C 30 seconds
2. 98°C 10 seconds
3. 52°C 30 seconds
4. 72°C 30 seconds
5. Move to step 2. 39 times
6. 72°C 5 minutes

